WEBVTT

03:00.880 --> 03:02.214
Hi, sir.

03:02.216 --> 03:03.448
Just this.

03:04.551 --> 03:05.584
Four.

03:06.920 --> 03:08.187
Thank you.

03:22.669 --> 03:26.271
<i> Furthermore</i>
<i> this indemnification clause</i>

03:26.273 --> 03:29.508
<i> clearly states that there</i>
<i> will be no injunctive relief.</i>

03:30.710 --> 03:35.247
And our client's chances
of being rewarded

03:35.249 --> 03:37.916
financially are minimal
at best.

03:41.521 --> 03:43.722
I'll finish it tomorrow.

04:33.473 --> 04:33.472
<i> Can I be blamed for feeling</i>

04:33.474 --> 04:37.609
<i> that things were a little</i>
<i> strange that night?</i>

04:40.813 --> 04:44.750
<i> You don't expect</i>
<i> a power outage</i>
<i> in the spring.</i>

04:44.752 --> 04:46.852
<i> Not without a storm first.</i>

05:00.933 --> 05:03.302
<i> When you're tired</i>
<i> and it's a long day</i>

05:03.304 --> 05:05.504
<i> and you're trying</i>
<i> to get home</i>

05:05.506 --> 05:08.607
<i> you tend to feel all these</i>
<i> little disconnects</i>

05:08.609 --> 05:12.344
<i> as the slow trajectory</i>
<i> of a collapsing civilization.</i>

05:14.047 --> 05:16.548
<i> At least that's where I go.</i>

05:47.947 --> 05:52.017
<i> "In the suburbs,</i>
<i> we live in nature."</i>

05:52.019 --> 05:53.885
<i> That's a quote</i>
<i> from my realtor</i>

05:53.887 --> 05:55.954
<i> the selling phrase she used</i>
<i> when Diana and I</i>

05:55.956 --> 05:57.956
<i> first looked at this place.</i>

05:58.891 --> 05:58.890
Oh, crap.

05:58.892 --> 06:03.962
<i> And you do see</i>
<i> deer, rabbits, crows.</i>

06:03.964 --> 06:06.365
<i> But we don't live in nature.</i>

06:07.467 --> 06:09.768
<i> That's the point</i>
<i> of the suburbs.</i>

06:09.770 --> 06:12.437
<i> You live apart from humans.</i>

06:12.439 --> 06:14.740
<i> And you're protected</i>
<i> from what's wild.</i>

06:14.742 --> 06:16.708
Jesus.

06:16.710 --> 06:18.577
Go on, get out of here.

06:18.579 --> 06:19.711
Go on!

06:20.980 --> 06:22.981
Go on, get out!

06:25.952 --> 06:27.753
Oh, damn it.

06:35.962 --> 06:37.496
Oh, Christ.

06:49.108 --> 06:51.109
Oh, god. Damn it.

07:00.486 --> 07:01.620
Damn it.

07:03.589 --> 07:05.023
Alright.

07:48.968 --> 07:50.969
Ha! Ha! Go on.

08:47.126 --> 08:49.728
<i> I had quarreled with my wife.</i>

08:51.798 --> 08:54.165
<i> We did this thing</i>
<i> where we would play</i>

08:54.167 --> 08:55.667
<i> at sexual jealousy.</i>

08:59.605 --> 09:00.906
But anyway, um..

09:00.908 --> 09:03.008
<i> Or I played at it</i>

09:03.010 --> 09:05.010
<i> and she was my accomplice.</i>

09:05.012 --> 09:07.846
<i> After 15 years of marriage</i>

09:07.848 --> 09:09.948
<i> jealousy was</i>
<i> the reliable stimulant.</i>

09:11.951 --> 09:11.950
<i> Let's be honest.</i>

09:11.952 --> 09:17.088
<i> When your spouse gets</i>
<i> jealous, it's flattering.</i>

09:17.090 --> 09:20.258
<i> The blood stirs,</i>
<i> the heart pounds.</i>

09:20.260 --> 09:23.061
<i> We'd quarrel..</i>

09:23.063 --> 09:25.897
<i> ...and we'd have sex.</i>

09:25.899 --> 09:29.768
<i> Or as Diana would say</i>
<i> provocatively</i>

09:29.770 --> 09:31.803
<i> we'd fuck.</i>

09:31.805 --> 09:31.803
<i> And it works.</i>

09:31.805 --> 09:34.940
The guy you were coming
onto all afternoon.

09:34.942 --> 09:34.940
<i> Until it doesn't.</i>

09:34.942 --> 09:37.909
Obviously, I wasn't
coming on to him --

09:37.911 --> 09:39.611
oh, yeah, obviously.

09:39.613 --> 09:42.047
Well, Diana,
anyone within 10 feet

09:42.049 --> 09:43.982
could see what was going on.

09:43.984 --> 09:45.984
Well, who was watching?

09:45.986 --> 09:47.652
It was a conversation.

09:47.654 --> 09:50.088
I witnessed
the whole thing, Diana.

09:50.090 --> 09:52.824
You were practically
issuing him an invitation.

09:52.826 --> 09:55.660
Only in your peculiar
imagination, Wakefield.

09:55.662 --> 09:57.729
Meanwhile,
you'll chat up any woman

09:57.731 --> 09:59.631
who even looks at you
and I'm the one who --

09:59.633 --> 10:02.367
no, no, no. You made
a very suggestive remark.

10:02.369 --> 10:03.835
I made an amusing remark.

10:03.837 --> 10:05.236
Oh, amusing? Ah!

10:05.238 --> 10:07.238
Everyone laughed but you.

10:07.240 --> 10:10.175
Well, I failed
to be entertained
by watching my wife

10:10.177 --> 10:13.044
come onto a guy
in a Polo shirt.

10:14.380 --> 10:16.214
I was replying
to something he said.

10:16.216 --> 10:20.151
Something stupid
if you must know..

10:20.153 --> 10:20.151
God!

10:20.153 --> 10:25.223
I am so sick of this --
this constant surveillance.

10:25.225 --> 10:25.223
- You --
- whoa, whoa, whoa --

10:25.225 --> 10:28.960
no, you have muzzled me
to the point where I can't

10:28.962 --> 10:31.129
carry on a conversation
with other parents.

10:31.131 --> 10:32.931
I barely relate
to people anymore --

10:32.933 --> 10:36.101
- you were relating to him.
- What do you not see?

10:36.103 --> 10:38.269
I mean, do you think
I'd be even remotely
inclined to start

10:38.271 --> 10:40.805
something up
with anyone given
the relationship we have?

10:42.642 --> 10:45.010
All I want..

10:45.012 --> 10:47.112
...is to get through the day.

10:47.114 --> 10:50.649
That's what I think about.
Just get through the day.

11:40.833 --> 11:42.200
Unbelievable.

11:53.112 --> 11:55.313
<i> Why go in there now?</i>

11:55.315 --> 11:58.349
<i> Just to endure another</i>
<i> predictable scene</i>
<i> with my wife.</i>

11:59.318 --> 12:01.319
<i> Soon enough,</i>
<i> they'd all be asleep.</i>

13:00.079 --> 13:01.412
Oh.

13:11.123 --> 13:12.257
Oh.

13:13.994 --> 13:15.260
Oh, shit.

13:16.228 --> 13:18.263
Shit! Ah!

13:20.966 --> 13:22.267
<i> Oh, god.</i>

13:25.271 --> 13:26.437
Oh!

13:36.115 --> 13:38.449
<i> You know, frankly</i>
<i> I was totally bewildered</i>

13:38.451 --> 13:41.019
<i> by this situation</i>
<i> I had created for myself.</i>

13:43.190 --> 13:46.057
<i> Diana would probably think</i>
<i> I'd been with someone else.</i>

13:47.393 --> 13:48.893
<i> Not that I had ever</i>
<i> given her a reason</i>

13:48.895 --> 13:51.229
<i> to doubt me</i>
<i> in 15 years of marriage.</i>

13:52.331 --> 13:53.998
<i> Oh, my god.</i>

13:54.000 --> 13:57.001
<i> It would be</i>
<i> the weakest of tactics</i>

13:57.003 --> 13:59.370
<i> for me to walk into my house</i>

13:59.372 --> 14:01.105
<i> and try to explain to her</i>

14:01.107 --> 14:02.941
<i> the perfectly</i>
<i> rational sequence</i>

14:02.943 --> 14:05.310
<i> that led me to spend</i>
<i> the night in the garage.</i>

14:14.220 --> 14:16.287
<i> You know,</i>
<i> another woman might have</i>

14:16.289 --> 14:19.190
<i> saved my supper plate</i>
<i> in the refrigerator.</i>

14:19.192 --> 14:22.293
<i> But I lived</i>
<i> in Diana's judgment.</i>

14:22.295 --> 14:24.996
<i> It shone on me</i>
<i> as in a prison cell</i>

14:24.998 --> 14:27.465
<i> where the light</i>
<i> is never turned off.</i>

14:32.605 --> 14:35.206
<i> The immediate solution?</i>

14:35.208 --> 14:38.509
<i> Postpone my entrance 'til</i>
<i> my wife had gone off to work.</i>

14:47.887 --> 14:49.420
Mm.

14:51.258 --> 14:52.924
Rush, rush, rush.

15:01.034 --> 15:03.034
The bus is here, girls.

15:04.503 --> 15:06.204
Hey, hey, hey, hey.

15:06.206 --> 15:08.172
They forgot their lunches.

15:11.377 --> 15:12.911
<i> Girls, girls, lunch.</i>

15:14.179 --> 15:16.447
<i> They're gonna be late again.</i>

15:18.251 --> 15:20.385
Bye-bye, girls.
Have a good day.

15:20.387 --> 15:22.053
<i> Okay, love you.</i>

15:30.462 --> 15:32.063
Oh, yeah.

15:32.065 --> 15:35.500
<i> The first call</i>
<i> would be to my office.</i>

15:35.502 --> 15:37.402
<i> No, he hasn't come in.</i>

15:38.637 --> 15:40.204
<i> No.</i>

15:40.206 --> 15:43.441
Yesterday evening.

15:43.443 --> 15:46.044
Well, no,
he didn't say anything.

15:47.513 --> 15:49.647
Mm-hmm. Well, he left around
the usual time.

15:51.550 --> 15:53.584
<i> Oh, yes, of course, I will.</i>

15:55.220 --> 15:56.421
Bye-bye.

16:05.264 --> 16:07.198
Oh, where are you going now?

16:15.207 --> 16:17.575
Surprise, car's still there.

16:26.585 --> 16:28.419
The plot thickens.

16:42.768 --> 16:45.136
<i> After a few calls</i>
<i> to her friends</i>

16:45.138 --> 16:47.438
<i> wouldn't it seem reasonable</i>
<i> to expect</i>

16:47.440 --> 16:50.708
<i> that the assistant curator</i>
<i> of the county museum</i>

16:50.710 --> 16:52.543
<i> would depart for work?</i>

16:54.013 --> 16:56.781
<i> I realize this is</i>
<i> a common enough complaint.</i>

16:56.783 --> 16:59.784
<i> But there are times when I</i>
<i> feel I've spent my life</i>

16:59.786 --> 17:01.352
<i> just waiting for my wife</i>

17:01.354 --> 17:03.421
<i> to get ready</i>
<i> to leave the house.</i>

17:12.297 --> 17:15.532
Oh, you got to be
fuckin' kidding me.

17:41.727 --> 17:43.061
Oh.

17:58.577 --> 17:58.576
What the hell?

18:03.348 --> 18:05.416
Wait a minute, wait a minute
wait a minute.

18:11.557 --> 18:12.690
Ah-ha!

18:14.694 --> 18:16.127
Yeah.

18:24.336 --> 18:25.503
<i> Ah-ha.</i>

18:26.738 --> 18:27.839
Yes, officer.

18:28.707 --> 18:30.508
<i> No checks were missing.</i>

18:31.710 --> 18:33.678
<i> Why, why! Where could he be?</i>

18:36.748 --> 18:38.249
<i> Ah. Oh.</i>

18:39.418 --> 18:41.486
There's the hubs.

18:41.488 --> 18:43.688
No wonder you want him back.
He's a stud.

18:51.163 --> 18:54.465
<i> Our town police</i>
<i> are well-paid and polite</i>

18:54.467 --> 18:56.501
<i> and not so different</i>
<i> from the rest of us</i>

18:56.503 --> 19:00.371
<i> in their distant relationship</i>
<i> to actual crime.</i>

19:01.608 --> 19:03.474
<i> Nobody mugged him</i>
<i> or anything.</i>

19:14.520 --> 19:15.853
What? What am I,
a travel agent?

19:20.692 --> 19:22.160
<i> I guarantee</i>
<i> he's at the strip club</i>

19:22.162 --> 19:24.162
<i> right now hangin' around.</i>

19:24.730 --> 19:26.164
Dickhead.

