20:16.381 --> 20:17.648
Shit.

20:24.289 --> 20:26.991
<i> But then god help us.</i>

20:27.759 --> 20:29.560
<i> The widow, babs.</i>

20:30.262 --> 20:31.729
<i> Right on cue.</i>

20:33.265 --> 20:34.332
Christ.

20:43.742 --> 20:44.875
<i> Oh, god.</i>

20:46.745 --> 20:48.746
Do you ever shut up?

20:51.016 --> 20:54.485
<i> No, no, no, no.</i>
