right here.

21:08.033 --> 21:09.967
Broad shoulders.

21:09.969 --> 21:11.802
Like a fuckin' linebacker.

21:14.039 --> 21:16.807
I'll be here for you.

21:16.809 --> 21:18.509
<i> But, darling,</i>
<i> now is the time</i>

21:18.511 --> 21:21.379
that you need
to protect yourself.

21:21.381 --> 21:22.947
You do.

21:22.949 --> 21:24.815
Financially, I mean.

21:29.888 --> 21:31.889
<i> He could wipe you out.</i>

21:31.891 --> 21:33.924
<i> Oh, no, no, no.</i>

21:33.926 --> 21:38.529
