21:59.418 --> 22:00.718
Oh, god, I wish I had

22:00.720 --> 22:02.586
a high-powered rifle
right now.

22:04.657 --> 22:05.856
<i> One shot.</i>

22:08.694 --> 22:10.928
That woman could be up here
for two days.

22:45.865 --> 22:49.667
<i> At this juncture,</i>
<i> it seems fair to point out</i>

22:49.669 --> 22:52.002
<i> if your spouse</i>
<i> had seemingly vanished</i>

22:52.004 --> 22:54.538
<i> would you go off</i>
<i> to work as usual?</i>

22:54.540 --> 22:57.375
<i> Are daily matters</i>
