23:06.385 --> 23:07.985
<i> Leave it to Mrs. Wakefield</i>

23:07.987 --> 23:09.954
<i> to turn a rather</i>
<i> amusing sidestep</i>

23:09.956 --> 23:11.956
<i> into prima facie evidence</i>

23:11.958 --> 23:14.825
<i> of Howard's</i>
<i> thoughtless behavior.</i>

23:14.827 --> 23:16.927
<i> I was naive</i>

23:16.929 --> 23:19.964
<i> and condescending</i>
<i> to her mother.</i>

23:19.966 --> 23:22.032
<i> I lacked interest</i>
<i> in her work.</i>

23:22.034 --> 23:25.736
<i> Or I wasted perfectly</i>
<i> beautiful full weekends</i>

23:25.738 --> 23:27.805
<i> watching football games.</i>

23:27.807 --> 23:30.040
<i> And if she was</i>
<i> such a feminist</i>

23:30.042 --> 23:32.109
<i> why did my opening</i>
<i> a door for her</i>

23:32.111 --> 23:36.013
<i> or helping her on</i>
<i> with her coat</i>
<i> matter so goddamn much?</i>

24:04.576 --> 24:06.877
<i> Standing there</i>
<i> in the clear light of day..</i>

24:08.447 --> 24:10.648
<i> I could see.</i>

24:10.650 --> 24:14.051
<i> Diana felt that she</i>
<i> had married the wrong man.</i>

25:19.284 --> 25:20.584
Oh.

25:23.788 --> 25:23.787
<i> I ask you</i>

25:23.789 --> 25:28.893
<i> what is so sacrosanct about</i>
<i> a marriage and a family</i>

25:28.895 --> 25:32.663
<i> that you should have to live</i>
<i> in it day after day</i>

25:32.665 --> 25:34.965
<i> however unrealized</i>
<i> that life may be?</i>

25:51.750 --> 25:55.019
<i> Who hasn't had the impulse</i>
<i> to just put their life</i>

25:55.021 --> 25:56.787
<i> on hold for a moment?</i>

25:58.089 --> 25:59.223
<i> I ask you.</i>

26:26.918 --> 26:28.819
Mm.

26:28.821 --> 26:30.988
<i> Oh, my god, that looks good.</i>

26:35.860 --> 26:37.995
<i> What are you two</i>
<i> doing laughing?</i>

26:39.164 --> 26:41.231
Assholes.

26:41.233 --> 26:44.234
Unh-unh-unh.
Here's the conspiracy.

26:44.236 --> 26:47.037
<i> It's all a little too</i>
<i> convenient, don't you think?</i>

26:47.039 --> 26:49.640
Oh, yes, I agree.

26:49.642 --> 26:51.642
I think she's totally guilty.

26:52.911 --> 26:54.712
