just stoppin' by
for a little deli.

27:12.898 --> 27:14.798
Hello, Ben.

27:14.800 --> 27:16.800
<i> You're not fooling anybody.</i>

27:20.872 --> 27:23.173
<i> I say, without shame</i>

27:23.175 --> 27:26.176
<i> I'd given not</i>
<i> a single thought</i>
<i> to anyone at work.</i>

27:27.912 --> 27:30.180
