32:26.544 --> 32:28.011
<i> Oh.</i>

32:31.582 --> 32:32.950
Come on back.

32:34.152 --> 32:35.719
Come on, honey, come back,
come back.

32:35.721 --> 32:37.521
Come back,
come back, come back.

32:39.691 --> 32:41.525
<i> There you are.</i>

32:44.229 --> 32:46.697
<i> About my wife's</i>
<i> deliberate nudity.</i>

32:48.132 --> 32:50.200
<i> Apparently</i>
<i> it's a side effect of her</i>

32:50.202 --> 32:52.736
